author: Mitsuru Obe
title: Trans-Pacific Partnership Pact Likely to Further Consolidate Japanese Farms
text:
TOKYO—The Trans-Pacific Partnership trade deal would likely spur further restructuring in Japan’s calcified agriculture sector, accelerating a push toward consolidation of small farms and a shift toward premium exports.
